short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: CodeInsights is a browser extension that provides code insights for GitHub repositories.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: CodeInsights is an easy to use browser extension that provides comprehensive insights into the code within GitHub repositories. It allows developers to quickly gain a better understanding of their project's codebase and make informed decisions on how to improve it. With CodeInsights, developers can gain deep insights into their codebase and make more informed decisions on how to improve it.
